description:
This week's issue of Doctor Who Adventures is one of grossest and slimiest ever, as we take a look at the yuckiest aliens that the Doctor has ever met!

It's also packed with puzzles, monster info, more comic adventures, a scary snowman mask and facts about the Great Intelligence!

Is love hell? This book answers to that question.

The first book in the ridiculously and painfully depressing series, collecting Life in hell-comic strip series.
name: Love is Hell

description:

No, not really. It makes you even more certain of it.

description: A coming of age issue. Mi Ling retreats to a lake to cleanse herself and discovers something more than she expected. Meanwhile her friend, Zhen, senses that Mi Ling will stop at nothing to find the perpetrators and goes on the look out for the Bao Gang returning with more than Chinese whispers.

When the dragon finally awakes it strikes at the heart of a friendship! Mi Ling knows the truth and goes to look for her dearest friend, but Zhen has ulterior motives, and due to the fear of his enraged father, goes on the prowl to stop a secret that has been protected by the villagers for almost 13 years. The Bao Gang, now on a seek and destroy mission, catch up with Mi Ling and Zhen to try to silence them.
